# ImageModel リファクタリング計画

## 目的

現在の [HeaderProfile](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#156-194) / [HeaderPrimary](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#114-154) / [HeaderSpectrogram](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#22-112) / [SpectrumBase](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/spectrum.py#18-59) という入れ物クラス群を廃棄し、  
`la-cosmic` プロジェクト ([stis_la-cosmic/src/stis_la_cosmic/image.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/la-cosmic/stis_la-cosmic/src/stis_la_cosmic/image.py)) を参考に  
**[ImageUnit](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/la-cosmic/stis_la-cosmic/src/stis_la_cosmic/image.py#18-45) → [ImageModel](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#23-97) → [ImageCollection](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#99-139)** の 3 層構造へ再編する。

---

## 現状の問題点

| 問題 | 詳細 |
|---|---|
| [HeaderProfile](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#156-194) / [SpectrumBase](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/spectrum.py#18-59) が薄いラッパー | ほぼ属性を持ち運ぶだけで、ロジックがほとんどない |
| [SpectrumBase](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/spectrum.py#18-59) 単体で `wave_array` が取れない | 波長情報は [HeaderSpectrogram](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#22-112) に閉じており不自然 |
| FITS 書き出し時に header/data が分離 | 将来の [write_fits](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/la-cosmic/stis_la-cosmic/src/stis_la_cosmic/image.py#605-643) 実装で困難になる |
| 二重ネスト参照 | `image.header.spectrogram.wavelength_array` のように深くなる |

---

## 競合・影響分析（変更前の現状確認）

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 以下のコード箇所が、廃棄クラスを **直接参照** しているため、すべて変更が必要になる。

### [processing/velocity.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity.py)（影響大）

```python
# L214: ImageModel.header.spectrogram を使用
wavelengths = image.header.spectrogram.wavelength_array

# L215-216: ImageModel.spectrum を使用  
data = image.spectrum.data
n_spatial = data.shape[1]

# L232: ImageModel.header.spectrogram を使用
spatial_pixels = image.header.spectrogram.spatial_array
```

→ リファクタリング後は `image.wavelength_array`（プロパティ）と `image.sci.data` に変更。

### [processing/image.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py)（全面書き換え対象）

```python
from .header import HeaderProfile       # → 廃棄
from .spectrum import SpectrumBase      # → 廃棄

class ImageModel:
    header: HeaderProfile               # → primary_header / sci(ImageUnit)
    spectrum: SpectrumBase              # → sci, err, dq に分解

# plot_spectrum 内
wave = self.header.spectrogram.wavelength_array  # → self.wavelength_array
self.spectrum.data[:, point]                      # → self.sci.data[:, point]
```

### [processing/__init__.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/__init__.py)（エクスポート整理が必要）

```python
from .header import HeaderProfile   # → 削除
from .spectrum import SpectrumBase  # → 削除
```

`__all__` からも [HeaderProfile](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#156-194), [SpectrumBase](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/spectrum.py#18-59) を削除する。

### [tests/test.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/tests/test.py)

```python
image_collection = ImageCollection.from_readers(reader_collection)
```

現在の [from_readers](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#113-130) シグネチャと互換性があるので **変更不要**。  
ただし [ImageModel](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#23-97) の内部 API が変わるため、`VelocityModel.from_image` 経由で間接的に影響あり。

---

## 廃棄クラス一覧

| クラス | ファイル | 処理 |
|---|---|---|
| [HeaderPrimary](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#114-154) | [header.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py) | 廃棄（属性は `ImageModel.primary_header` に吸収） |
| [HeaderProfile](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#156-194) | [header.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py) | 廃棄（[from_reader](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/spectrum.py#43-59) ロジックは `ImageModel.from_reader` に統合） |
| [HeaderSpectrogram](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#22-112) | [header.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py) | 廃棄（[wavelength_array](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#67-93) / [spatial_array](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#94-112) は [ImageModel](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#23-97) プロパティへ） |
| [SpectrumBase](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/spectrum.py#18-59) | [spectrum.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/spectrum.py) | 廃棄（`data/error/quality` は `sci/err/dq: ImageUnit` に分解） |

