## 提案変更内容

### [processing/image.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py) ← 全面書き換え

#### 新 [ImageUnit](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/la-cosmic/stis_la-cosmic/src/stis_la_cosmic/image.py#18-45)

```python
@dataclass(frozen=True)
class ImageUnit:
    data: np.ndarray
    header: fits.Header

    def to_hdu(self) -> fits.ImageHDU: ...
```

#### 新 [ImageModel](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#23-97)

```python
@dataclass(frozen=True)
class ImageModel:
    primary_header: fits.Header
    sci: ImageUnit               # HDU 1 (科学データ)
    err: ImageUnit | None        # HDU 2 (誤差)
    dq:  ImageUnit | None        # HDU 3 (品質フラグ)

    @classmethod
    def from_reader(cls, reader: STISFitsReader) -> Self: ...

    @property
    def wavelength_array(self) -> np.ndarray:
        """WCS から波長配列を計算する [m]"""
        ...  # HeaderSpectrogram.wavelength_array のロジックを移植

    @property
    def spatial_array(self) -> np.ndarray:
        """空間方向のピクセルインデックス配列"""
        ...  # HeaderSpectrogram.spatial_array のロジックを移植

    @property
    def shape(self) -> tuple[int, int]:
        return self.sci.data.shape

    def plot_spectrum(self, point, center_wave, width, ax) -> Axes: ...
```

> [!NOTE]
> [wavelength_array](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/header.py#67-93) の計算には `sci.header` の WCS 情報を使用する。  
> (現 `HeaderSpectrogram.wcs` → `WCS(sci.header)` に相当)

#### [ImageCollection](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#99-139) は内部実装のみ変更

シグネチャ（[from_readers](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#113-130)・[__iter__](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#137-139)・[__getitem__](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/la-cosmic/stis_la-cosmic/src/stis_la_cosmic/image.py#746-748)・[__len__](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/la-cosmic/stis_la-cosmic/src/stis_la_cosmic/image.py#743-745)）は変えないため、  
**[tests/test.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/tests/test.py) と [velocity_map.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity_map.py) は変更不要**。

---

### [processing/velocity.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity.py) / [processing/velocity_map.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity_map.py) ← **変更しない**

データフローが大幅に変わるため、[VelocityModel](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity.py#143-319) / [VelocityMap](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity_map.py#24-257) は今後しばらく使用しない。  
コードはそのまま残すが、[__init__.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/util/__init__.py) の公開 API からのみ除外する。

> [!NOTE]
> これらのファイルは旧 [ImageModel](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/image.py#23-97) の API（`.header.spectrogram.*`, `.spectrum.data`）を参照したままになるが、使用しないため今は修正しない。

### [processing/__init__.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/__init__.py) ← エクスポート整理

