[velocity.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity.py) / [velocity_map.py](file:///Users/r.hisada/astroresearchs/ThreeDimensinalStructure/STIS_imaging_spectrograph/spectrum_package/src/spectrum_package/processing/velocity_map.py) のファイル自体は残す（削除しない）。

